ji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7684de68eabe87bdf1e9724e35c4a90d10580602","tid":795371,"uid":22554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T03:35:03.000Z","msg":"佢地只係想幫地鐵, 巴士公司用少D 錢係電費度, 其他野佢地得鬼閒理"},{"pid":"9b0f5a9b87f8672f7d9da93f501fda788ef50c9c","tid":795371,"uid":127807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"85f91e3a640b8c1f73208d667dc0ad6f8c9293eb","tid":795371,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T03:33:59.000Z","msg":"懷疑環保撚有份炒bitcoin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T03:39:00.000Z","msg":"歪憂牙希牙?! <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ff279b112851b27b261bedfb7fb120349fde9d","tid":795371,"uid":54337,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T03:46:55.000Z","msg":"&lt;五問環保撚&gt;<br />\n<br />\n1）開機掘比特幣，浪費電力，環保撚點解唔呼籲叫人停止？<br />\n<br />\n2）農曆新年，廢老鍾意換新銀紙嚟封利是。新銀紙來自新木材，係來自伐木。環保撚點解唔呼籲叫人停止？<br />\n<br />\n3）香港人狂去旅行，一年去幾次日本，飛機引擎狂噴廢氣，加劇溫室效應，點解環保撚唔出聲叫人唔去旅行？<br />\n<br />\n4）廢老初一十五清明重陽生忌死忌，鍾意燒衣紙。<br />\na. 衣紙來自紙張，來自伐木<br />\nb. 燒紙增加co2 <br />\nc. 衣紙五顏六色，燒時有毒<br />\n點解環保撚唔出聲叫人停止？<br />\n<br />\n5）香港地產商賣樓，個個地產mk經紀，派卡片，派售樓書，全部都係紙張。<br />\n環保撚入中式酒樓搗亂，叫人唔好食魚翅。<br />\n點解唔企喺樓盤展銷會示範單位外，出聲叫人停止派卡片同售樓書？"},{"pid":"14fa1171113b28dde2e669eee5b28fe4e1d672a1","tid":795371,"uid":17866,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"89ff279b112851b27b261bedfb7fb120349fde9d","tid":795371,"uid":54337,